---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AC Repair Newport Beach | HiLo Heating and Air" description="Expert AC repair in Newport Beach, CA. Coastal HVAC specialists who understand salt air corrosion. Same-day service from HiLo Heating and Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AC Repair Newport Beach</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Living that close to the coast has its perks — and its downsides. The salt air that makes Newport Beach gorgeous also eats away at outdoor AC units faster than you'd expect.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">AC Repair Services in Newport Beach</h2>

        <p>Living that close to the coast has its perks — and its downsides. The salt air that makes Newport Beach gorgeous also eats away at outdoor AC units faster than you'd expect. So when something goes wrong, it's usually not random — there's a coastal reason behind it. That's where HiLo Heating and Air comes in, handling <strong>air conditioning repair Newport Beach</strong> homeowners need whenever the heat (or the salt corrosion) finally catches up with their system.</p>

        <h2>Coastal Conditions Mean Different Wear and Tear</h2>
        <p>Inland AC units and coastal ones don't age the same way. Out here, condenser coils corrode faster, electrical connections get finicky, and components that would last a decade elsewhere sometimes need attention in half that time. Our techs see this constantly — it's a big part of why <strong>air conditioning repair Newport Beach</strong> isn't quite the same job as repair work twenty minutes inland. We know what to check first, because we've seen the same failure patterns over and over in homes just like yours.</p>

        <h2>Common Issues We Run Into</h2>
        <p>Some calls are simple — a tripped breaker, a dirty filter choking airflow. Others take more digging: a refrigerant leak that's slowly killed cooling performance, a capacitor that finally gave out, a compressor on its last legs. Most <strong>air conditioning repair Newport Beach</strong> visits land somewhere in that range — weak airflow, a system short-cycling, or a unit that just won't turn on at all. We diagnose it properly before quoting anything, because guessing wrong means you pay twice.</p>

        <h2>We Don't Make You Wait</h2>
        <p>When your AC dies on a hot day, "we'll see you next week" isn't really an answer. Most repairs get same-day or next-day appointments, and our trucks are stocked with the parts that actually fail most often around here — corrosion-related stuff, mostly. That means <strong>air conditioning repair Newport Beach</strong> jobs usually wrap up in one visit, not two or three.</p>

        <h2>Local Techs Who Know the Area</h2>
        <p>Being based nearby isn't just convenience — it means our team already understands what salt air, humidity, and ocean proximity do to HVAC equipment over time. Every job is done to code, backed by a guarantee, and handled by people who'll still be around if something needs a second look later. That's the real value behind hiring a local company instead of someone driving in from out of the area.</p>
        <p>If your AC's struggling — short on power, blowing warm air, or just refusing to start — give HiLo Heating and Air a call. We'd rather diagnose it right the first time than have you calling back next month.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Why does my AC seem to break down more often living near the beach?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Salt air speeds up corrosion on outdoor units, especially coils and electrical connections — it's just part of coastal living.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How fast can someone come out?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same-day, sometimes next-day during busier periods.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Is it actually a repair, or do I need a new system?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Most issues are repairable — we'll diagnose it on-site before talking about replacement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Will I know the price before work starts?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, you'll get a quote upfront, no surprises on the invoice afterward.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How often should coastal homes get their AC inspected?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">We'd recommend twice a year given the corrosion risk — once before summer, once mid-season if possible.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you work on all brands?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, central air, ductless mini-splits, heat pumps — most major brands found in Newport Beach homes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are your technicians licensed and insured?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every technician is fully licensed and insured.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What if the problem comes back after a repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">That's covered under our guarantee — just reach out and we'll take care of it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
